results.description: Neymar is booed by his own fans throughout his Paris St-Germain return but scores an injury-time overhead kick to beat Strasbourg.

results.title: Neymar booed by own fans on PSG return in win over Strasbourg

results.description: Eric Maxim Choupo-Moting is guilty of arguably the worst miss ever as PSG squander the chance to wrap up the Ligue 1 title.
results.title: Eric Maxim Choupo-Moting sitter costs Paris St-Germain early title

results.description: Paris St-Germain forward Neymar told "don't go blubbering" after leaving the pitch in tears after suffering a fractured metatarsal
results.shortTitle: Neymar in tears after foot injury

results.description: Cesc Fabregas has a home debut to forget for Monaco as Thierry Henry's side are beaten 5-1 by Strasbourg.
results.title: Monaco 1-5 Strasbourg: Cesc Fabregas' first home game ends in heavy defeat

results.title: Strasbourg 1-1 PSG: Champions held again but are 14 points clear

results.title: Charlie Wyke: Sunderland sign Bradford City striker on undisclosed terms
